- cache [:help_headers] do
  %h1= t('.header')
  %h2 This site is for the #{@tenant.subdomain} Unicycling Convention registration
  %h3 FAQ

.help_text
  %ul
    %li
      %b I cannot Log in:
      Once you have Signed Up, check your e-mail for a confirmation message. Check all spam filters. Choose "Resend Confirmation E-mail" if you cannot find the e-mail
    %li
      %b> Translations
      \: I found a missing/mistake in a translation. Submit the translation details here in the 'feedback', or apply to be a translator, and help do more of the translations for a language.
    %li
      %b How do I Register:
      Once you have signed in, choose "Create New Competitor" or "Create New Non-Competitor" and fill out the fields.
      %br
      Pay for the registration in order to secure your registration
    %li
      %b How to share Registration Details:
      As a Team Captain or Club leader you can request access so that you can pay for other members' registrations, as well as see the events that they have signed up for
      %br
      - if signed_in?
        Request access to your team's registrations through the #{link_to "Registrant Access Request", user_additional_registrant_accesses_path(@user)} Form
If you have any problems or questions about registration, please submit feedback below:
%br
= render "feedback"
